name: Wrapped eETH
description: Ether.fi's eETH is a decentralized, non-custodial liquid staking token that enables Ethereum holders to earn staking rewards while maintaining full liquidity and control over their assets. eETH along with its wrapped non-rebasing version, weETH, integrates seamlessly with the Ethereum ecosystem, offering users a flexible and secure way to contribute to network validation and participate in the DeFi space.
